{"tha-ap118:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap118:0.2":"Mahaparivaravagga ","tha-ap118:0.3":"Citakapujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap118:1.1":"“Vasami rajayatane, ","tha-ap118:1.2":"samacco saparijjano; ","tha-ap118:1.3":"Parinibbute bhagavati, ","tha-ap118:1.4":"sikhino lokabandhuno. ","tha-ap118:2.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap118:2.2":"citakam agamasaham; ","tha-ap118:2.3":"Turiyam tattha vadetva, ","tha-ap118:2.4":"gandhamalam samokirim. ","tha-ap118:3.1":"Citamhi pujam katvana, ","tha-ap118:3.2":"vanditva citakam aham; ","tha-ap118:3.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap118:3.4":"sakam bhavanupagamim. ","tha-ap118:4.1":"Bhavane upavitthoham, ","tha-ap118:4.2":"citapujam anussarim; ","tha-ap118:4.3":"Tena kammena dvipadinda, ","tha-ap118:4.4":"lokajettha narasabha. ","tha-ap118:5.1":"Anubhotvana sampattim, ","tha-ap118:5.2":"devesu manusesu ca; ","tha-ap118:5.3":"Pattomhi acalam thanam, ","tha-ap118:5.4":"hitva jayaparajayam. ","tha-ap118:6.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap118:6.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap118:6.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap118:6.4":"citapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap118:7.1":"Ekunatimsakappamhi, ","tha-ap118:7.2":"ito solasa rajano; ","tha-ap118:7.3":"Uggata nama namena, ","tha-ap118:7.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap118:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap118:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap118:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap118:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma citakapujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap118:10.1":"Citakapujakattherassapadanam chattham. "}